If an interrupt happens during a BRK, then the end of the BRK will be <strong>replaced</strong> with the end of the interrupt.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Fri Sep 30, 2005 6:54 pm</p><hr />
